            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "I am ready to align with and allow calm, grounded mornings as my new default. I allow it now. I allow it now. I allow it now.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
